  "description": "ORBITAL's warm-red orbit feeds OPAL via AudioToWavetable, then OPAL applies freeze-and-granularize: EnvToDecay coupling from ORBITAL's envelope holds opal_freeze at 0.75 whenever ORBITAL notes sustain. The granulator orbits the frozen ORBITAL snapshot at 120ms grain size, density=18. shimmer=0.55 adds crystal architecture to ORBITAL's analog warmth. When ORBITAL releases, freeze dissolves and new material flows into the buffer. Catch → crystallize → release → catch again.",
